[SET COMMENTS]

<p>A lot like the last set, except with Swords Dance this time over Choice Band.</p>

[Other Options]

<p>Growth and Synthesis, but don't use them, they are just the other mediocre moves Shiftry learns. Better go with the above sets.</p>